description: I was really surprised when he told me that he was from the Ukraine. His Czech was so fluent when we spoke on the telephone that I wouldn´t have even guessed he could come from somewhere else. Obviously he lived here already quite long and together with his girlfriend he shared a flat with 2 more roommates. But since they left his problems started. He couldn´t find a replacement fast enough and when the first rent was due he started to lend money. And so on and so on. Now, as he is in trouble he called me. He was kinda handsome. He worked as a shop-assistant and he also looked like like a nice shop-assistant. He was afraid of having to leave the Czech Republic if he couldn´t pay back his debts so I made him an irresistible offer...
title: Debt Dandy 115
